          <actionDesc>Introduced in Senate</actionDesc>
          <name>Introduced in Senate</name>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Income-Based Repayment Debt Forgiveness Act</strong></p> <p>Amends the Internal Revenue Code to exclude from gross income, for income tax purposes, income imputed from the discharge of student loan indebtedness pursuant to a federal program that provides for income contingent or income-based repayment of such loan. </p>]]></text>
        </item>
